name: Applying pressure
description: Dang that felt good. I wanted to see if my achilles & cardio could handle some solid pace/force. I was really hoping I could hit a sub 5 for the 6k loop so I way exceeded my own expectations. Stoked! Upping the pace for the last 2k while already tired felt awesome & very attainable.
